  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Hemispatial neglect is a disorder where the patient has difficulty attending to objects and
      information in the left side of space, which occurs following strokes to the right side of
      the brain. This project is designed to help us understand how optokinetic stimulation treats
      the symptoms of hemispatial neglect.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
